name: Alien51
description:
You wake up in a cell in some kind of laboratory... it seems you are not even in your own planet. You can feel that your ship is close, you know that if you get to it you can escape and they don't know that if you concentrate... can teleport.

  • WASD - Move
  • Left click - Teleport
  • ESC - Pause
